    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sweet potato wedges are cooking, trim and finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger </strong>and <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Separate your <strong>coriander</strong> from your <strong>mint</strong>, then strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stalks and roughly chop the leaves (discard the stalks)</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
