    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>Thai-style pork patties</strong>,<strong> </strong>press down firmly with a spatula and cook for 5 min</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3? You may need to do this in batches!</p><p>Flip the <strong>Thai-style pork</strong> <strong>patties</strong> and reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 5 min further until cooked through and charred (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
