      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and finely slice your <strong>radishes</strong></p><p>Peel lengths off your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-purple\">[6]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8] </span>wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced radishes</strong> and <strong>cucumber ribbons </strong>to a bowl with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime wedge[s]</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Gently mix it all together – this is your <strong>quick-pickled radish salad</strong></p>",
